This is the to do file. A list of objectives the writer of the script want to implement
1. RPM - 
     A. Create RPM version

2. Script Security - 
     A. Ensure only root and/or the netsecure user can execute the daemon

3. Expand to VPN networks
     A. Create a method to detect new/foreign network objects on vpn networks

4. Logger
     A. Make use of logger instead of using written logging entries

5. ...
